The Case of the Visiting Sultan

deck: Suicide 5 is a 120 page hard cover graphic novel from Bughouse Comics. It is about five people willing to die for what they perceive to be immortality. The graphic novel also features a Season's End short story.
description: Glenn was just watched by thousands committing suicide online. With Glenn's death, a new...terrifying game begins.
Translates : Gambit (2012) #15-16 , Wolverine (2013) #13 , Savage Wolverine (2013) #12
Translate : Uncanny X-Force (2013) #13-15 , Amazing X-Men (2014) #03

deck: SEASON'S END is a 120 PAGE HORROR/FANTASY hardback book mixing prose with original paintings creating a non-traditional graphic novel.
description: The world has grown dark and magic has become tainted and dangerous. A young man, Mimdal, is the last living priest that can perform the miracles of old. He and his protector, the soldier Adrielle, are enlisted to find out why the gods have fallen silent. Along with the brutish Dunlari and his savage captive, Grib, the dark wizard Falhern, and Lidderly, the secretive bard, they seek the terrible truth. The new gods have come.
name: Season's End
Walt Disney's The Sword in the Stone

description: Our 2nd monthly compilation for Comixology of Aces Weekly: the exclusively digital comic art magazine featuring some of the world's finest creators of comic art. Published by David Lloyd, the guy who brought you V For Vendetta.
name: Volume 02

description: The Council has stepped out of the shadows with game-changing results, and Amelia's back is against the wall! On Omega Company hits the town just in time for a big monster party! But did Amelia get her invite?

volume.name: Amelia Cole and the Enemy Unleashed

description:
A Parting gift

Anya possesses a secret military technology that the government wants back at any cost! Anya and her friend Pete think they are out of danger until the mysterious Guardian shows up with a link to Anya's secret past that he promises will show Anya her true past.
name: A Parting Gift

description:
Atomic Robo is trapped in the year 1884. When he comes face-to-face with a plot that threatens to shatter the Americas, he's forced out of seclusion to become the Old West vigilante hero "Ironside."

Note: The digital edition (6/25/2014) for this issue was released before the print edition.
name: The Alamosa Massacre

volume.name: Atomic Robo: The Knights of the Golden Circle

description: There's a new Batman TV series on the air, but the Caped Crusader himself is not too happy about it. How will it affect his ability to fight crime?
name: Chapter Thirty-Seven

description:
Till Death Do Us Part

Keep your friends close, and your enemies closer. It's hard to tell who's who in a world riddled with crime, jealousy and deception. It makes it even more difficult to know who to trust when there's a $2 million dollar bounty on your heads. While Jack and Billy Blaze attempt to clear their names and prepare to leave the country, an unexpected attack on their family, at the House of Chen, culminates in an epic battle to the death.
name: Till Death Do Us Part

description:
The Mystifical Shambri-la

Bunk #2 (The Mystifical Shambri-la) picks up with Gorilla Max and his counterpart scheming along the shores of Sangfroidia. Thanks to a chance encounter with an old friend, Dean the Space Bean, Max and his monocular counterpart hitch a ride across the outer dimensions. A quick visit to the silent sidekick's home planet (Shambri-la) helps Max open a dialogue with a deeply-rooted inner voice - what's our simian to get out of all this, aside from a splitting migraine???...
name: The Mystifical Shambri-la

description: While a funeral takes place on the other side of town, Copernicus and his by-necessity compatriot, a robot crime boss who now lives in the body of one of his human enforcers, pay a house call.

ONE COMIC BOOK, THREE STORIES. WELCOME TO THE DOGHOUSE ISSUE THREE.

ITS NOT MY BLOOD.

The Hunt begins as Agents Holloway and MacGregor track down and stomp out a parasitic threat - in SPIDER.

YOURE A REAL GLASS IS HALF EMPTY KINDA GUY.

Dub Dub, another rather unorthodox cop, drops in - literally - and uncovers the kind of crime that could only happen - in NYPD WEIRD.

SOMEONE TOLD JACK THIS WONT WORK, RIGHT?

A blue collar repo man takes his team after white collar assholes, but things never quite go to plan for Jack Miller - in REPO DELUXE
name: Spider; N.Y.P.D. Weird; Repo Deluxe

description: The big meeting! All paths converge as the God Children all meet for the first time in over 100 years, Jerome finds his niece and all the while a dark figure continues to watch from the shadows.

It's the day of Senator Calloway's presidential announcement speech. Shawn and the team decide to join the senator on his big day and they plan to make it one he'll never forget. Find out what happens in the finale of the Calloway story arc!

Hostile human survivors capture Sarah and her friends in the ruins of New York City. But Abaddon and the ghosts of the spiritual realm aren't going to wait to see our heroes finished off. A turning point in the fate of the Earth takes place in the ensuing battle.

Note: The digital edition (6/25/2014) for this issue was released before the print edition.

In the thrilling finale of the very first Heartbreakers story arc, our heroes make a desperate push to complete their mission of getting their creator, Professor Sorenson, off Earth. Find out how Queenie got her famous scar!

Burma's latest story has him slinking through the filthy streets of 17th century London, trying, once again, to take over the world. But his...business partner has other plans. Meanwhile, Allison receives a cryptic warning, followed by a not-so-cryptic warning. What kind of danger is she in, and will she ignore the signs all around her? Things are escalating quickly in writer Paul Tobin (Bandette, Colder) and artist Benjamin Dewey's (The Tragedy Series) cat-astrophic tale!
name: Chapter Four

description: Witness the transformation. Witness the secrets of Mave. Witness the birth of Diamond. Open these pages and we'll start to see the truth behind the Gems and get a glimpse into the minds of creative geniuses Mary Jo Pehl (from Mystery Science Theater 3000) and CW Cooke (writer of VSS: Russian Roulette and Violet Rose). The comic event of 2013 continues here!
The gang are separated after an escape attempt. Lilith finds an old friend to help fight off those hungry beasties!

Money

Agent Morris' past converges with the woman he calls, "M3," shedding some more light on his obsessions with her. And a dangerous new assignment in Chicago may be the last one for our woman with the scar.
name: Money

description:
Sam Henderson (Scene But Not Heard, Spongebob Squarepants) returns to his long-running humor anthology for older readers with his cast of knuckleheads. Mr. He Aims to Please, Dirty Danny and Monroe Simmons all show up in this hilarious collection. Sex, drugs and Nancy comics all get sent up in the classic Henderson fashion. Back cover painted by Society of Illustrators 2014 MoCCA Arts Festival Award of Excellence winner Jess Ruliffson.

Note: The digital edition (6/25/2014) for this issue was released before the print edition.

With their star witness killed and another in a coma, Crockett and Tubbs must find another way to build a case against Pasqual. But after disagreeing on the evidence at the crime scene, Sonny and Rico are no longer seeing eye to eye. The Organized Crime Bureau team sets up protection for the final witness and Sonny gets a phone call from Pasqual's right hand man proposing a meet on their terms.

Having lost all hope in the heroes of his world, fate steps in and gives young Gavin Shaw the power to do the things they have not. Only as the teenage hero Midnight Tiger does his city have a chance at redemption.

"If you die and somehow end up in hell, I'll be right behind you."

The Sun family's plot to depose Lord Gaius and his sons has backfired. And while this could lead to Ryu breaking free of Sharon's enchantment, it is anything but a happy moment for Gene. Saul has gone full-on monster, slaughtering everyone in his path in an attempt to slake his thirst.

Succumbing to Sharon's last-ditch efforts, Ryu and Joseph can only watch helplessly as events unfold, but Gaius is coming to bail his boys out. Medusa, however, has other plans. She once again takes over Gene's body and confront Gaius about the sins of the past.
name: Vol. 13

description:
"If you die and somehow end up in hell, I'll be right behind you."

The Sun family's plot to depose Lord Gaius and his sons has backfired. And while this could lead to Ryu breaking free of Sharon's enchantment, it is anything but a happy moment for Gene. Saul has gone full-on monster, slaughtering everyone in his path in an attempt to slake his thirst.

Succumbing to Sharon's last-ditch efforts, Ryu and Joseph can only watch helplessly as events unfold, but Gaius is coming to bail his boys out. Medusa, however, has other plans. She once again takes over Gene's body and confront Gaius about the sins of the past.

THE THRILLING CONCLUSION TO THE SERIES!
name: Vol. 14

description:
Fire On The Mountain

The rescue has crash landed near the Basecamp, but don't realize they are being hunted.
name: Fire On The Mountain

description: Rumor 4: Three stories, telling aspects of the main Princess Ai saga from different points of view. Howdid Princess Ai rise to fame? How did Hikaru escape the wrath of both anti-Ai and pro-Ai fanatics? And what's up with Takeshi, anyway? Dig in for three helpings of Ai goodness!
name: Rumor 4

volume.name: Princess Ai: Rumors From the Other Side

description: Rampage vs. Mr. Walters. Winner takes all, but can a weakening Rampage overcome his most challenging foe to date or will he finally succumb after running through a gauntlet of super villains?

An ambush by the Undersheriff of Nottingham forces Robin to fight desperately for his very freedom. If he escapes with his life, danger still lies ahead in the forms of a betrayal from within his inner circle as well as a possibly more treacherous peril: the beginnings of young love.

It's a battle of wills between Slater and Jessie! Jessie's writing an article for the paper about how the cheerleading squad is underfunded, but Slater's being his usual pig-headed, macho self. And when arguments turn into dares, crazy things happen... Like Slater joining the cheerleading squad! Go Tigers!

Uncertainty Principle

Have you ever thought your teacher could be evil? Literally? Now that Ariel's magical abilities are awakened, she realizes the world around her is a little bit unusual. When she sees a black cloud hanging above her teacher, she convinces her neighbor Xigi to help investigate. And when they arrive at the teacher's house, a surprise awaits...
name: Vol. 2

description: Mayhem in the streets! Giant robots fighting giant cactus monsters! Total chaos! And yet none of it even registers to the heartbroken kid powerful enough to bring an end to the destruction. Unfortunately, he's fallen into the clutches of an even more insidious villain...
Now that Bonnies alive again, the girls plan to take Whitmore College by storm, starting with an Angels & Devils party the Omega Psis are throwing.
name: Frat Pack Part 1 of 3

description: The Vole with No Name has come to retrieve a priceless artefact from deep beneath Scum Hive, but Lord Marmot intends to make sure that he loses his mind in the most literal way possible. This volume includes the stories "Scum Hive", "The Vole That Dare Not Speak Its Name", and "A Vole By Any Other Name".
name: Scum Hive and Other Stories

description:
Quater-finals: Vegan Cat vs Flatwood Monster / Crimean Crab vs The Eye

The issue #0 presented all contestants, finally it's fight time. The clash features a fratricidal duel between two East European fighters - Crimean Cran and The Eye.

Vegan Cat shall learn some of the weak and strong points of Flatwood Monster. The favourite versus the enigma - it shall be a fascinating fight!

In the final issue, Claire and Victor have their ultimate showdown - but Victor has one more deadly trick up his sleeve. Jason returns to help, but his relationship with Claire will never be the same.

A new game is late for release, and to meet the deadline, one of the programmers decides to use code from an old game that seems to have the most realistic zombie characters he's ever seen. To the shock and horror of the new game's characters, the zombie enemies are less interested in being game targets than in eating digital brains!

It's off we go into the wild blue yonder to find out the origins from the most amazing air force in the world. Starting with the aerial exploits of balloons used in the Civil War for spying out the enemy, then tracing it to the dunes of Kitty Hawk, AMERICAN DEFENDERS: THE AIR FORCE shows how the United States Air Force keeps skies over the country safe and how they helped defeat any enemy - foreign and domestic.

Archer Coe is a performing hypnotist with the stage name "The Mind's Arrow." When his nightly shows are over, he moonlights as a special consultant for the rich and powerful. His latest client is a woman who claims to know him but whom he swears he's never met. Things take a strange turn for the worse when her husband ends up dead, and police suspect Archer of not just killing him, but also of being a sinister killer nicknamed "The Zipper." Archer has no memory of any of this, but it's making him doubt whether or not he's got blood on his hands. Could the master of other people's minds be losing his own?

Note: The digital edition (6/25/2014) for this volume was released before the print edition.
name: TPB

volume.name: Archer Coe and the Thousand Natural Shocks

description: Hunted by the law, starving and desperate, Athra agrees to defend a small village against Kaldgrani, a twisted and vicious killer. Although Athra initially plans to steal from the villagers and desert them, he finds himself falling in love with Hild, a beautiful young woman, and resolves to stay. Athra discovers, however, that the village contains additional mysteries when a strange woman appears claiming to know him and suddenly vanishes. When Kaldgrani attacks, all thought of that mystery is driven from Athra's mind as a brutal, running battle between them ensues. Will Athra survive to make a life for himself with Hild and solve the mystery that plagues him?
